item.title: HuskerBot Beta is Now Live

item.description: About Me Collin Dougherty is a M.S. mathematics student at UNO and works for UNMC doing data analysis for cancer research. He has several years of experience working with data on behalf of various Huskers coaching staffs. Feel free to connect with me on Github and Linkedin, leave your thoughts on my blog or share your ideas by writing me an email.
